[68.21, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# Three divergent overrides, one aligned, and a build-shaped handoff. Concerns aren't style preferences \u2014 they're declared technology contracts, and the skill caught the drift the author didn't know they introduced.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
